===Roulette===
The Roulette wheel is situated at the top of the coin pusher, and gives a chance at deploying medals or Sherbi Ball objects. The roulette can be triggered through perks and totems, and can also be bought with SP Medals, using the "Fever Roulette" skill, making the roulette earn more, and activating the Sherbi Chance Game. The shop to the left of the Skills Shop can also activate a timer for a "Faster Roulette" perk.

===Sherbi Lottery===
Sherbi Chance Game, Sherbi Jackpot, Sherbi Progressive Counter

Sometimes referring to as S-JACK.
===Paletta Lottery===
Paletta Chance Game, Paletta Jackpot, Paletta Progressive Counter

Sometimes referred to as P-JACK.

