====Auto-Play Pass====
Auto-Play Pass allows medals to be inserted automatically, instead of manually. Some perks and passive skills will not trigger with automatic insertion. Manually inserting medals while there is an elapsed timer on the Auto-Play Pass will only freeze the timer. The timer will continue counting down when manual insertion stops.

