== Altar and totems ==
Totems are passive skills that can be purchased with medals, and have varying benefits. Altars have to be purchased with medals first to place the totems. The shrine is located on the second floor. Effects from totems can stack with perks, other skills, and can compliment other totems. Finding the right combination of totems to use with each other is important to maximize medal earnings.
